Example of simple MPO geometry

* Environment
 Geant4 ver 11.3
 ROOT (v6.32.02)

 X-ray reflection physics codes are based on XRTG4.
 https://xraytracer.com
 Source codes are in source/src.
 These codes are partly modified for G4 11.3 and Lobster-eye MPO.

* How to build
 $ mkdir build
 $ cd build
 $ cmake ../source
 $ make
 $ make install

* How to run
 <Test with GUI> 
 $ cd TestBench
 $ ../bin/ex_mpo1
 ...
 Idle> /run/beamOn 10
 ...
 Idle> exit

 <Batch mode>
 $ ../bin/ex_mpo1 run_gpsGamma.mac

 <Plot PSF>
 $ python -i plt_psfsct.py

